    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained over the years. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the upholstery is clean and intact, showing only standard wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major electronics are fully functional. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that has plenty of life left.",
